title: Job well done and very satisfied
text:
We were very well satisfied with our landscape project that was performed by Palmetto Landscape locally owned too.

The whole crew knew their jobs and each guy made sure the home owner was satisfied with no short cuts .  They should all have shirts which states,  when your satisfied we are satisfied.    They cleaned up after the job well too.   Their equipment is fairly new and supplies were well in hand for every job.
           They Deliver with no Surprises!
